    <p>Qlik Sense OOB charts are responsive, so we want our extensions to be responsive as well. They should adjust themselves to fit whatever container they are asked to fill in a way that is useful and usable for the user. There are a couple of different ways we can modify our extension based on its size. Let’s review.</p></div><div class="col-xs-6 col-sm-6 col-md-6 col-lg-6 body-right"><div class="graph"></div></div></div></div><div id="section-1"class="section css-editor"><div class="row">
